`BitNet-MLX` is a standalone, edge-native mathematical processing engine developed by JuniorCloud LLC. It bypasses server bloat to translate high-dimensional dense continuous model manifolds ($FP16/BF16$) into absolute discrete operational matrices ($b1.58$ and $b1.0$). \
