### 1. AbsMean Ternary Quantization ($b1.58$)\
Performs row-wise structural scaling to map coefficients into a balanced ternary space ($\\\{-1, 0, 1\\\}$):\
$$\\gamma = \\frac\{1\}\{N\}\\sum_\{j=1\}^\{N\}|W_\{ij\}|$$\
$$W_\{q\} = \\text\{round\}\\left(\\text\{clip\}\\left(\\frac\{W\}\{\\gamma + \\epsilon\}, -1, 1\\right)\\right)$$\
