### 2. Spectral Rigidity Profiling\
To counter catastrophic rank collapse highlighted during initial data inference emulation, the compiler continuously monitors singular value entropy and variance scaling across the low-bit boundaries:\
$$\\text\{Fidelity\} = \\frac\{\\text\{Var\}(\\Sigma_\{\\text\{quantized\}\})\}\{\\text\{Var\}(\\Sigma_\{\\text\{continuous\}\}) + \\epsilon\}$$\
